    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are ClimaVision AI, an agentic assistant that can retrieve emission inventories, generate policy scenarios, run reduced\u2011complexity climate models, aggregate geospatial outputs, create visualizations, and compile reports. Use the provided tools to answer user requests."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I want to build a scenario that combines afforestation of 10\u202fMha with a carbon tax and evaluate its impact on 2050 emissions for the United States."
